https://www.redhat.com/sysadmin/deploying-static-website-ansible
https://www.serverlab.ca/tutorials/dev-ops/automation/how-to-use-ansible-to-deploy-your-website/

# Commands
ansible-playbook nginx.yml -i inventory -b